l|accessdate=2022-03-05|work=義大利廣播電視公司体育频道 (Rai News)|agency=義大利廣播電視公司|date=2022-03-04|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305162313/https://www.rainews.it/articoli/2022/03/pechino-inaugurate-le-paralimpiadi-la-tv-cinese-censura-lappello-per-la-pace-ucraina--550d1e55-6bdb-43d6-a2bf-9cc25fe09bde.html}}</ref>，最后还将安德鲁·帕森斯的致辭影片的回放从其网站和应用程序上删除<ref>{{Cite web|title=China censors anti-war comments during Paralympics opening ceremony|url=https://supchina.com/2022/03/07/china-censors-anti-war-comments-during-paralympics-opening-ceremony/|access-date=2022-03-08|date=2022-03-07|last=Harker|first=Gerry|work=SupChina|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308120410/https://supchina.com/2022/03/07/china-censors-anti-war-comments-during-paralympics-opening-ceremony/}}</ref>。

国际残奥委会当晚就安德鲁·帕森斯的发言被审查一事，要求中国中央电视台对此作出解释<ref>{{Cite web|title=Paralympic Body Asks China Why it Censored Anti-War Speech|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-05/paralympic-body-presses-china-on-censoring-of-no-war-speech|access-date=2022-03-05|work=www.bloomberg.com|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305105152/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-05/paralympic-body-presses-china-on-censoring-of-no-war-speech}}</ref>。隔日，国际残奥会发言人克雷格斯宾塞（Craig Spence）告诉《法新社》，他们已经等待了超过24小时，但仍然没有得到中国中央电视台的任何答复<ref>{{Cite web|title=War in Ukraine: the international committee accuses Beijing of censorship|url=https://www.world-today-news.com/war-in-ukraine-the-international-committee-accuses-beijing-of-censorship/|access-date=2022-03-07|date=2022-03-06|work=World Today News|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307075419/https://www.world-today-news.com/war-in-ukraine-the-international-committee-accuses-beijing-of-censorship/}}</ref>。北京残奥会的闭幕式上，安德鲁·帕森斯的发言再次遭到中国中央电视台的审查，其呼吁的「和平」口号和相关内容在转播节目中再次没有了翻译<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/cm-03142022132500.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-03-19 |archive-date=2022-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404035044/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/cm-03142022132500.html }}</ref>。

